==English==
===Etymology===
Ultimately from [[Proto-Indo-European]] '''*[[qwel]]''', with the notion of ''going around''

===Pronunciation===
*{{AHD|/wēl}}
*{{IPA|/wiːl/}}
*{{SAMPA|/wi:l/}}

